Living the high life: the loft and clever design tricks have turned this little Earls Courts apartment into a spacious home.
Former banker Joanne Leigh, with a passion for real estate renovation, went from a large house in Knightsbridge to an apartment in Earls Court in 2014 to a smaller one.
